{"tid":935453,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"柯個屎冇左兩舊水","createTime":"2018-12-10T04:29:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T05:15:21.000Z","uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"161a118bca51fe2f837c247deb1064c3dc2ae548","tid":935453,"uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T04:29:15.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n預左12點搭船過馬交<br />\n出門口肚痛柯左五分鐘屎 <br />\n落到西鐵 啱啱走左架車 要等5分鐘 <br />\n去到輕鐵站又送車尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要等八分鐘 <br />\n搞到我去到碼頭架船啱啱走 <br />\n依家要等到2點九同比多兩百蚊買過張飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果我唔柯屎可以慳返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a716ed164aa992ab35c1c46f6543a19dba3b5b","tid":935453,"uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T04:36:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b17520454673580eab0b149c3f2347c139617e5","tid":935453,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T04:37:08.000Z","msg":"點解要等到2點9"},{"pid":"abd9a1e84a332374a6ec5db8155764b715021803","tid":935453,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b17520454673580eab0b149c3f2347c139617e5","tid":935453,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T04:37:08.000Z","msg":"點解要等到2點9"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T04:38:31.000Z","msg":"應該屯門上船"},{"pid":"c6f1df23d68834e3b82e8595c9c73f7edc67f9ce","tid":935453,"uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abd9a1e84a332374a6ec5db8155764b715021803","tid":935453,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b17520454673580eab0b149c3f2347c139617e5","tid":935453,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyT